
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>15种bootstrap模态框动画弹出特效</title>

    <link href="~/MoTai/css/component.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    
    
</head>
<body>
    <div id="box">

        <a href="javascript:;" class="md-trigger btn btn-primary btn-sm" data-modal="modal-13">Show Me</a>
    </div>
    

    <div class="md-modal md-effect-13" id="modal-13">
        <div class="md-content">
            <h3>Modal Dialog</h3>
            <div>
                <p>This is a modal window. You can do the following things with it:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Read:</strong> modal windows will probably tell you something important so don't forget to read what they say.</li>
                    <li><strong>Look:</strong> a modal window enjoys a certain kind of attention; just look at it and appreciate its presence.</li>
                    <li><strong>Close:</strong> click on the button below to close the modal.</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="md-close btn-sm btn-primary">Close me!</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md-overlay"></div>
    <script src="~/assets/js/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/MoTai/js/classie.js"></script>
    <script src="~/MoTai/js/modalEffects.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
<script>
    show();
    function show() {
        var s = '<a href="javascript:;" class="md-trigger btn btn-primary btn-sm" data-modal="modal-13">Show Me</a>'

        $("#box").append(s);
    }
</script>